TLinkedList<T>.AddAfter(TLinkedListNode<T>,TLinkedListNode<T>) Method

Summary

Adds the specified new node after the specified existing node in the ILinkedList<T> .

Namespace: Spring.Collections.LinkedLists
Syntax
